title: No, Obama and former Italian Prime Minister Renzi didn't set up the U.S. election.
subtitle: A viral story that was broadcast about social media based on the theories of a mass fraud plot for voters.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: Former President Barack Obama of the United States "Order" of former Italian Prime Minister Mateo Rainzie to cooperate in a large-scale scheme of voter fraud to convert votes from Trump to Biden, four years in the future.
